                "sentiment": "positive"
            },
            {
                "observation": "In light of the challenges facing our city, I personally believe that it would do our city well to have a fresh pair of eyes bringing someone completely new that hasn't been here, that has no involvement or even alleged involvement in anything would be helpful. But that is when referring to someone in a permanent capacity as a permanent city administrator. I'm happy to hear that the search for city administrator is well underway. I look forward to seeing that on the agenda next week so we can move forward in securing a new permanent city administrator.",
