                "observation": "Today we're looking at an interim city administrator. And prior to assuming the role, ICA Merritt has in fact been the assistant city administrator. So, in looking at that decision, I do believe she was the logical choice in November. And I do believe she continues to be the logical choice today. I've heard from many of you that is not the issue that the people have. So I will be supportive of that.",
